<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.2">
<l>iṇṭaiyum puṉaluṅ koṇṭiṭai yiṉṟi yeḻumiṉō toḻutumeṉ ṟimaiyōr</l>
<l>aṇṭarum parava varavaṇait tuyiṉṟa cuṭarmuṭik kaṭavuḷtam kōyil</l>
<l>viṇṭalar tūḷi vēyvaḷar puṟavil viraimalark kuṟiñciyiṉ naṟuntēṉ</l>
<l>vaṇṭamar cāral māliruñ cōlai vaṇaṅkutum vāmaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Come, simple heart; we will worship at Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l rend="indent">on whose slope bees nestle in the scented nectar</l>
<l>Of fragrant blooming cone flowers in the verdant uplands</l>
<l rend="indent">where thick bamboo extends to the sky,</l>
<l>The temple of the god with a radiant crown who sleeps on a serpent bed,</l>
<l rend="indent">as unblinking [celestials] and gods praise him,</l>
<l>Saying, “Oh, rise; we will worship without cease with garlands and water.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
